<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">س هـ ر:</span> <span class="c2">(السَّهَرُ)</span> الْأَرَقُ وَبَابُهُ طَرِبَ فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(سَاهِرٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(سَهْرَانُ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(أَسْهَرَهُ)</span> غَيْرُهُ. وَرَجُلٌ <span class="c2">(سُهَرَةٌ)</span> كَهُمَزَةٍ أَيْ كَثِيرُ السَّهَرِ. وَ <span class="c2">(السَّاهِرَةُ)</span> وَجْهُ الْأَرْضِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>